rows.label: tlk47100071_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Blimey. Talk about a missed
opportunity...

rows.label: tlk47100071_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Eh? You can understand me?!
Heh, life's full o' surprises.

rows.label: tlk47100071_02_msg0003
rows.name:
A pretty Blade who used to come
round this way croaked it, I heard.

rows.label: tlk47100071_02_msg0004
rows.name:
She tried petting me once, but I bolted
off. Would've been nice in retrospect...

rows.label: tlk47100071_02_msg0005
rows.name:
She could've pet me and I'd've rolled
on my back and everything would've
been cushty. But c'est la vie...
